commit.message: Fixed bug in MyIterator::operator[]() where m_pos wasn't accounted for.
Fixing that wxCmdLineEntryDesc changed from wxWidgets 2.8 -> 2.9/3.0
Test building with wxWidgets 3.0 on Travis.
Adding an iterative mergesort variant, which merges level-wise bottom up.
Fixing warnings by making variables unsigned ints.
Adding Batcher's Bitonic and Odd-Even Merge Sorting Networks by recording and reordering swap sequences.
Adding simple command line filter for sorting-test to filter algorithms.
Fixing small bug in MSD radix sort for bucket size = 1.
Running test cases on travis as well.
Adding sorting-test to test correctness of all sorting algorithms.
Separating WSortView into (virtual) SortArray and (painting) WSortView.
Fixing useless warnings in various files.
fix use of private stdlib-function
Building with travis.
Publishing version 0.6.5
Using QueryPerformanceCounter() on Win32 to get microsecond array access delay.
